    - rid: 107151359355650108
      type: {class: WeighedChoice, ns: , asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        modules:
        - weight: 50
          module:
          - rid: 107151359355650109
          - rid: 107151359355650110
          output: 'The order is given and our followers mobilize. Barricades, buckets,
            and every precaution are employed to keep the waters at bay. When the
            storm finally breaks, the homes of the faithful lie in ruins, but the
            damage to our temples is minimal. Upon seeing our sanctuaries standing
            pristine amidst the wreckage, the people attribute it to divine providence.

            [Gained
            20 Zeal & 40 Flock]

'
        - weight: 45
          module:
          - rid: 107151359355650111
          - rid: 107151359355650112
          - rid: 107151359355650113
          output: 'Good news! We managed to minimize the damage to our temples. However,
            the populace accuses us of prioritizing material wealth over the lives
            of our followers. We shall have to toil hard to cleanse this stain from
            our reputation.

            [Gained 10 Zeal & 20 Flock Lost 15 Bliss]

'
        - weight: 5
          module:
          - rid: 107151359355650114
          - rid: 107151359355650115
          - rid: 107151359355650116
          output: 'The wrath of the Beholder is directed at us! The districts where
            our temples stand are the hardest hit by the deluge. Our men drown while
            attempting to defend the holy sites, which are destroyed regardless.
            The people take note of our misfortune. Has the Beholder forsaken us?

            [Lost
            40 Wealth, 10 Zeal & 15 Bliss]

'
